  "body": "Reconciliation phase:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"536\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-03-08 at 3 10 52 am\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/810438/23688588/6f36e206-03ad-11e7-9b4f-bbb4b4183e09.png\">\r\n\r\nCommit phase:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"757\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-03-08 at 3 11 42 am\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/810438/23688518/fc03b052-03ac-11e7-8cff-177eef4943ee.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\nShould work with all Fiber features, including error boundaries and incremental deferred work.\r\n\r\nDeferred work example:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"635\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-03-08 at 3 13 15 am\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/810438/23688545/32dc38e2-03ad-11e7-930a-589ac319c51a.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n- [x] Basic implementation\r\n- [x] Don't display bailed fibers\r\n- [x] Show deferred work sensibly\r\n- [x] Include lifecycles\r\n- [x] Naming and style\r\n- [x] Always clear marks and measures\r\n- [x] Replace stack with a field\r\n- [x] Fix Flow\r\n- [x] Gate by DEV\r\n- [x] Host effects\r\n- [x] Track cascading updates\r\n- [x] Check the overhead and decide whether to always emit measurements or not\r\n  - [x] I tried my best\r\n  - [x] Gonna test it soon\r\n- [x] Verify in different browsers\r\n- [x] Write tests maybe? Or at least shim it in tests?\r\n- [x] Verify edge cases work:\r\n  - [x] Nested subtrees\r\n  - [x] Error boundaries\r\n  - [x] Uncaught errors\r\n- [x] What else?",
